{"type": "article", "id": 22445, "title": "半月结构书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-18T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113119TyVkAdUHm1jSMBJe.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">瑞典设计事务所 Note Design Studio 带来了一组带有半月结构的书架。书架的外形方正简单，在镂空的两侧加上了半月式的弯曲结构，有点像倒立的拱。当光线照射在上面时，会产生弧线的阴影，就像在墙上印出了花纹。它的实现了功能的最大化，还带给书架一份优雅的古典色彩。<a href=\"http://www.fogia.se/en/product/cabinets-storage/arch-2/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071131173FDIp7iV6QtkJLsZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113117X6I4cjZeiuHzrtVv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071131185B6G8bgOPEvWCdfK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113118hKr4DUg8LpH1BZnO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113119QN8hEjkS1DoLcC0V.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}